**ecosis Laboratories** is a ***Decentralized Autonomous Organization*** as a  *Community Driven Enterprise* participating to Web 3.

We are Web 3 Experts developing, consulting, designing, investing and publishing Web 3 Projects. We help partners to launch their Organizations - their own Enterprises.

Partners can hire eLabs Experts to startup Web 3 Projects. 

### Approach

Everything shall be reusable. Everything shall be automated.

We want an easy to use tool-set for the accessibility to build your own platform, which is scalable and customizable.

_data.text:
## Network

**eLABs** ***Tokenomics*** is running on the [Polygon Technology](https://polygon.technology/) and is deployed via [Aragon](https://aragon.org/).


## ELABS Token

*ELABS* Token is a **Governance Token**. You can use it for

- having Vote Weight
- writing Proposals
- getting Insights
- having the status of being an ***ecosis Laboratories Member***

This Token is especially stunning for

- Developers
- Engineers
- Investors
- Asset Managers
- Content Creators
- Exclusive Community

and of course everyone who is interested into the project.

> Total Supply only 3,000,000!

### Rewards and Bounties by initial Distribution

Contributors get rewarded by ELABS Token out of *Reward Pool* until all Reward Tokens are fully distributed!

Contributions are:

- Development
- Content Creation
- Investments

and more the DAO finds interesting.

After the full distribution contributors get rewarded via *Bounties* or *Proposals* out of *Reward Treasury*. This treasury is filled by the revenue stream of *ecosis Projects* and *Investments*

#### Token Allocation

- 40% Reward Pool
- 30% Initial Supply (Tokensale)
- 30% Genesis Reward Pool

##### Genesis Rewards

Initially 10 Members are hired and get rewarded by by the ***Genesis Pool***. Each gets 10% of the Genesis Pool, so 3% of the total supply.

_data.text:
> Token Holders become official *eLabs Members*

*eLabs Members* have exclusive access to hidden channels, can publish *Proposals* and have *Vote Weight*.

## Genesis Members

> Genesis Members are selected Professionals at the very beginning

*Genesis Members* work on internal Projects like

- DAO Operator
- Business Development
- Asset Management
- Community Management
- Smart Contract Engineering
- Component Development
- Campaign Developer
- Public Relation
- Law/Policy
- Research

These Members are a kind of the core Team behind ***ecosis Laboratories***.

## Contributors

*Contributors* can participate to programs like

- Bounties
- Grants
- Fixes Issues

and any other job offering coming to this network.

They get rewarded and help this institution to improve and grow. When a *Contributor* gets rewarded with ***ELABS*** Token, she, he or the contributing institution become officially a *eLabs Member*

## Investor

An *Investor* gets insights of ***ecosis Laboratories*** and become an official *eLabs Member*.
